Calendar of consideration of the State Duma of tax projects from November 5 to 21, 2019
06 Nov 2019, 05:35 by Arkady Bryzgalin



Sensations, it seems, are not expected ...
On October 24, at the plenary meeting of the State Duma, draft resolution No. 819290-7 “On the calendar for consideration of issues of the State Duma from November 5 to 21, 2019” was approved, according to which the following bills on amendments to legislative acts in the field of taxation and financial law will be considered:

On the draft federal law No. 775302-7 “On amendments to Art. 33333 of the Tax Code of the Russian Federation regarding the establishment of the size of the state fee for entering information about a legal entity in the state register of pawnshops2 (reviewed by the Council of the State Duma on 11.09.19);
On the draft federal law No. 723363-7 “On Amendments to Article 126 of the Tax Code of the Russian Federation” (on establishing liability for failure by the taxpayer to submit information to the tax authorities on the creation of a separate division of the organization) (reviewed by the Council of the State Duma on 10.07.19, 21.10.19 - a decision was made to consider the bill in accordance with part 7 of article 11 of the Rules);
About the draft federal law No. 790096-7 "On amendments to Art. 381 of Part II of the Tax Code of the Russian Federation ”(on the abolition of privileges on tax on property of organizations in relation to federal highways and structures that are their integral technological part) (reviewed by the Council of the State Duma on September 25, 19);
About the draft federal law No. 794241-7 "On amendments to chap. 26.1 of Part II of the Tax Code of the Russian Federation ”(on changing the procedure for paying USHN) (reviewed by the Council of the State Duma on September 25, 19).
